### Install a runtime family at host level
POST http://localhost:7878/api/v1/backends/llama.cpp/install HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "version": "b4970",
  "accelerator": "cuda12"
}

### Response 202
HTTP/1.1 202 Accepted
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {
    "install_id": "ri_9f3a1c2e",
    "install_task_id": "it_4e11a802",
    "progress_channel": "runtime:install:it_4e11a802"
  },
  "error": null
}

### Response 409 — already installed
HTTP/1.1 409 Conflict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ALREADY_INSTALLED",
    "category": "conflict",
    "message": "llama.cpp b4970 cuda12 is already installed as ri_9f3a1c2e"
  }
}

### Response 404 — unknown family
HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "FAMILY_UNKNOWN",
    "category": "validation",
    "message": "No runtime family registered for 'foo-engine'"
  }
}
